{"word":"ἔκβασις","slug":"ἔκβασις","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἔκβασις</b></el> <el>(ἔκβᾰσις, εως) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἐκβαίνω'><el>ἐκβαίνω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>a way out, egress</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>a going out of, escape from</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}